challah for hunger challah for hunger at stanford home about cfh resources winter 2012 donation recipients welcome to the website for challah for hunger cfh at stanford challah for hunger at stanford is sponsored by the jewish students association and the hillel at stanford every week we bake fresh challah and donate the proceeds to a variety of social causes check out some of the groups we sponsor on the left orders are currently closed check back spring quarter if you were unable to pickup you prepaid challah on thursday please pick it up in the student activities room which is on the second floor of the koret pavillion the building behind hillel on the row pick up your loaves by 9pm on friday or else they will be given away thanks
